Package: luci-app-node-tunnel
Version: 1.0.0-1
Depends: libc, luci-base, luci-compat, cloudflared, frpc
Source: feeds/luci/applications/luci-app-node-tunnel
SourceName: luci-app-node-tunnel
License: MIT
Section: luci
Architecture: all
Installed-Size: 32000
Description: LuCI frontend for Node Tunnel - local proxy (sing-box/xray) with Argo and FRP reverse proxy publishing.
 Supports both Cloudflare Argo Quick Tunnel (no account required) and Permanent Tunnel
 (via token), plus FRP TCP/HTTP/HTTPS/UDP tunnels.
